1. optimized images in tinypng and jpeg optimizer (70%, 54%).
2. made smaller copies of background for tablets and laptops (1023px, 480px)
3. cut all @keyframes from animate.css except used ones (fadeInLeft fadeInRight, fadeInDown, fadeIn) (73kb to 4kb)
4. minimized some scripts
5. moved styles from sections starting second to last to secondary.css and loaded on window load
6. moved media queries to separate file that loads only on screen width less than 1023
7. no need in async/defer